node.title: Prince William and Kate Middleton release family Christmas card
node.alt: Prince William, Duke of Cambridge and Britain's Catherine, Duchess of Cambridge with their three children.
node.description: The Duke and Duchess of Cambridge release a new family photo of the royal couple and their three children, taken during a trip to Jordan earlier this year.
node.content: ["The Duke and Duchess of Cambridge have released a new family photo of the royal couple and their three children, taken during a trip to Jordan\u00a0this year.", "The photo shows Prince William and Duchess Kate sitting with Prince George, 8, Princess Charlotte, 6, and Prince Louis, 3.", "Kensington Palace said the family photo would feature on the Cambridges' Christmas card this year.", "Details of when the family trip took place have not been made public.", "The photo is in contrast to last year's Christmas card which showed them gathered at their family home in Norfolk, England.", "While it was not stated who took the photo, the Duchess has become known for publicly releasing her original photography, which has featured portraits of her family and documentation of royal trips abroad.", "Reuters/AP"]
